BR Partners, a Brazilian financial-
advisory firm founded by a former Goldman Sachs Group Inc.
executive, was granted licenses to operate as a bank and a
brokerage,  Veja magazine  reported, without saying where it got
the information.  The licenses were given by the Brazilian central bank, Veja
said. BR Partners was founded in 2009 by Ricardo Lacerda, former
